{"tid":1650421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟今日生日 有少少嘢想講","createTime":"2019-10-13T03:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:28:23.000Z","uid":181257,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5570ae96df416e6aa2ee2c4147bc8ebb81e205d3","tid":1650421,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"相信好多真香港人同我一樣，今日生日都唔會慶祝，亦無心情。因為有好多正事要做。<br />\n<br />\n有一少部分人，係見朋友出自己又出，出到去有講有笑，影相打卡，嘉年華撚，大家之前應該見過。<br />\n<br />\n唔需要為呢班人影響到自己，因為佢地根本唔係同路人，完全唔需要介意佢地，只要自己做好自己本分就足夠。時間真係唔多，場運動已經冷卻緊，我哋要加大力度參與，各有各做，啲無謂人就唔好理了。<br />\n<br />\n今日生日對我黎講無特別，但係今日13號係開花日，對全香港人就好重要，一陣見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361ccf832468d11f67be93bccccf844f9a7206e7","tid":1650421,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeOohC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeOohC.png&h=b72c0b46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSTC04i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSTC04i.png&h=0066384c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90pe3hE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90pe3hE.png&h=2a11879d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96c8a30e3116a15c8e4c164067e062075795d913","tid":1650421,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:04:55.000Z","msg":"和理開花一齊搞"},{"pid":"0cdba16c1cb5960834d87c9ecb8bbe590189125a","tid":1650421,"uid":180503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"兄弟 生日快樂"},{"pid":"4f1b1d8158661166b13f5224526a0f188422545a","tid":1650421,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"和理開花一齊搞"},{"pid":"73a177c06f45ea4f1a56fc62f8455d81527c4148","tid":1650421,"uid":203332